title: Fall Aesthetics
description: Fall Aesthetics is a beauty game where you need to prepare your fashion for the fall season. Unlock your inner fashionista to style the crew around the globe. Create unique outfits inspired by the dynamic streets of New York, the warm, golden sunsets of Tuscany, the captivating festivities, the timeless elegance of Japan, and the enchanting allure of Scotland! Get ready for the fall fashion!
